{"tid":1036953,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"頸淋巴痛 喉嚨有痰/異物好耐","createTime":"2019-02-25T14:49:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-12T17:37:28.000Z","uid":225882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6d4612f26aa3bf45e6ea705d19b9d385b2c36eb3","tid":1036953,"uid":225882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T14:49:16.000Z","msg":"我近一兩個月 下顎附近淋巴有兩三次痛（今日發覺又有）同埋頸一向會摸到有淋巴結<br />\n喉嚨好似有痰/異物 咁兩個月左右 食完野後特別有感覺 但係吐唔到出黎 有睇一次街症話我喉嚨發炎<br />\n今日再睇左 話開多次藥比我  有無巴絲試過 <br />\n我其實係咪應該去睇耳鼻喉科<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a2737398181d5cb04e72867983c587757853480","tid":1036953,"uid":29070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T14:51:45.000Z","msg":"淋巴癌症狀"},{"pid":"84b8433cc79fc123ce148f7a5f709cf3d259c633","tid":1036953,"uid":225882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6a2737398181d5cb04e72867983c587757853480","tid":1036953,"uid":29070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T14:51:45.000Z","msg":"淋巴癌症狀"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T14:58:10.000Z","msg":"唔撚係掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d5aff716cee56f3082ea0be18740c4376dd3678","tid":1036953,"uid":141917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"84b8433cc79fc123ce148f7a5f709cf3d259c633","tid":1036953,"uid":225882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6a2737398181d5cb04e72867983c587757853480","tid":1036953,"uid":29070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T14:51:45.000Z","msg":"淋巴癌症狀"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T14:58:10.000Z","msg":"唔撚係掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T17:37:28.000Z","msg":"食咗咩藥，之後點？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}